questions.quote: Uh, JFK. [To Elaine] I need some small bills for a tip. You got anything?
Don't flatter yourself, my friend. I'm here strictly for material, and I have a feeling this is a potential gold mine.. I still think you're nuts, though.
Great, great. So anytime you want you can just visualize her naked.
We have a bonus reality stop today. We will be hauling muffin stumps to the local repository.
"Believe it or not, George, isn't at home, please leave a mes-saaage at the beep. I must be out or I'd pick up the pho-one. Where could I be? Believe it or not, I'm not hooome."
I hate rental cars. Nothin' ever works: the window doesn't work, the radio doesn't work... and it smells like a cheap hooker... [pause] Or is that you?
But, I - I didn't know what she was talking about. I couldn't hear her!
One second... Well, if it would make you feel better I could speak to Dr. Whatley. I have to go back and have a wisdom teeth removed.
Why should I be uncomfortable just because my apartment is closer to town hall than yours?
If you were in the mafia, would you tell her every time you killed someone?
